headline: 2 Reasons to Watch IR and 1 to Stay Cautious
summary: Over the last six months, Ingersoll Rand shares have sunk to $82.99, producing a disappointing 8.8% loss - worse than the S&P 500’s 1.1% drop. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
